nodes.text: Flib was a Caarite, who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.

Flib was a child during the time of the Clone Wars and lived on Caarimon, the Caarite homeworld. When the Shistavanen Blik landed the Z-95 Headhunter Ku'Amo in Joventusek on Caarimon, Flib went and played around the ship, along with a group of other Caarite children. A short time afterwards, Flib traveled to Dorumaa, in the Cularin system, to attend a celebration that was being held in honor of the heroes of Cularin.
